name: Exile city #01 The onlookeer
description: The onlooker stood on the ledge, an old aircraft fuselage inhabited by raiders lay beneath. She surveyed the distant city and the path that lay between them. She would have to use the cover of night to evade the gangs that surrounded the city, waiting for their next victims. K19x sat patiently, his processors buzzing just waiting to for the command to serve his master above all else. The light of the city pulsed invitingly, the sound of distant machinery droned in the background, peppered with the echo of gunshots. What she saw in front of them was Exile City...
